data.title: Trains to Carlisle Cathedral
data.meta_description: Check out the nearest station to Carlisle Cathedral and book your cheap train tickets with Trainline. It's easy to travel by train to Carlisle Cathedral.
data.text:
Carlisle station is a major station with taxis usually available on a rank. Advance booking is not normally necessary or even possible, unless arriving early in the morning or late at night. Operators who may accept bookings include:

Beeline (01228 534440) or

City (01228 520000) or

Metro (01228 522088).
